<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="wherever-adv">wherever <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /weər'evə(r)/    美 /wer'evər/  </p>
<p>[用于问句，表示惊讶]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>究竟在哪里：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Wherever did you find that beautiful sweater? 
你到底在哪里发现那件漂亮的毛衣的？</p></div></div>